{"tid":687621,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"香港97前vs97後，和港英前vs港英後，係兩回事","createTime":"2018-06-02T12:03:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-02T16:30:23.000Z","uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"7dc195d8546edbb5d257734d8c83d44b418254d2","tid":687621,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T12:03:53.000Z","msg":"香港97前，97後<br />\n同香港港英前，港英後<br />\n係兩樣野<br />\n<br />\n香港97前好，定97後好，<br />\n受科技因素影響最大。<br />\n<br />\n你cut左你寬頻上網account, 賣左你所有智能手機平板電腦，換返部黑白手提電話，頂到幾年就會知。<br />\n<br />\n仲有，因為當年（1997年）科技係幾落後，所以罪惡率遠比現在多，校園欺凌亦比現在嚴重，黑社會問題大，衛生環境亦比現在差。<br />\n<br />\n除非你真係好討厭 I.T. 和科技，否則好難想象你會覺得香港在1997年前會比1997年後好。<br />\n<br />\n至於港英好，定特區好（只談政權計）<br />\n因為時代和科技進步左，<br />\n所以好難比較，<br />\n真係比較，你移民去英國本土住下幾年好就知道。<br />\n<br />\n不過多數認為，論經濟管理、政治和協調能力，港英政府比特區政府出色。"},{"pid":"8083b8127424a990d757594891671284c7cad630","tid":687621,"uid":48083,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T12:12:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/02/201254_27b966e033e6c9c01d75d521a671bc4f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F02%2F201254_27b966e033e6c9c01d75d521a671bc4f.png&h=dda047f5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/02/201255_2bb6462ae424dfb2ba5896d81eedf583.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F02%2F201255_2bb6462ae424dfb2ba5896d81eedf583.png&h=954382b0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/02/201256_5735c8df5ec5523cc37b77aa6f30b94f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F02%2F201256_5735c8df5ec5523cc37b77aa6f30b94f.png&h=a6777546&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/02/201256_4aa7e2ba58f7da701a0bf44b8c9d53e2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F02%2F201256_4aa7e2ba58f7da701a0bf44b8c9d53e2.png&h=ea36512c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ce3e59e30737ec8d03bfcc32deaa9485e65305ac","tid":687621,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T12:22:21.000Z","msg":"如果你問我<br />\n<br />\n港英定特區好<br />\n答案：港英<br />\n<br />\n香港1997前，定1997後好<br />\n答案：1997後<br />\n<br />\n香港回歸前好，定回歸後好<br />\n答案：回歸後"},{"pid":"153e0e82981197117ebf41b3c5071aada198e3c8","tid":687621,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"8083b8127424a990d757594891671284c7cad630","tid":687621,"uid":48083,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T12:12:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/02/201254_27b966e033e6c9c01d75d521a671bc4f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F02%2F201254_27b966e033e6c9c01d75d521a671bc4f.png&h=dda047f5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/02/201255_2bb6462ae424dfb2ba5896d81eedf583.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F02%2F201255_2bb6462ae424dfb2ba5896d81eedf583.png&h=954382b0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/02/201256_5735c8df5ec5523cc37b77aa6f30b94f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F02%2F201256_5735c8df5ec5523cc37b77aa6f30b94f.png&h=a6777546&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/02/201256_4aa7e2ba58f7da701a0bf44b8c9d53e2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F02%2F201256_4aa7e2ba58f7da701a0bf44b8c9d53e2.png&h=ea36512c&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T12:25:31.000Z","msg":"不服的話。如果你仲係覺得97前好。<br />\n<br />\n麻煩你試一試下，先賣左你部智能手機和平板電腦，之後 cut左你屋企的寬頻上網account先。相機唔好用數碼相機，一定要用傳統返菲林相機。<br />\n生活返3、5、7年，感受下無網生活。<br />\n<br />\n如果唔係，你就係享受緊97後的科技生活，又係度吹奏97前生活的無賴，唔該收皮。"},{"pid":"bade01613597d99f65b3d99a5bcc052977f0f4e6","tid":687621,"uid":19005,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T12:27:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 假膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d89cb46e9fe2b4d894922d4e00ef3d8c89295756","tid":687621,"uid":15205,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T16:30:23.000Z","msg":"有無人可以講下港英時期點美好法？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/686521/page/6?ref=ios\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/686521/page/6?ref=ios</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n條五毫錄音機黎嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}